  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of the study is to determine if there is a difference in the number of
      women with a complete miscarriage after 10 days between expectant management versus treatment
      with 800 micrograms of misoprostol intravaginally in women with an an incomplete miscarriage
      before 14 weeks and a gestational sac retained in the uterus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
