      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  nonviable intrauterine pregnancy with retained gestational sac in the uterus

          -  the embryo if visible 5 to 35 mm without a heart beat

          -  vaginal bleeding

          -  circulatory stable

          -  hemoglobin at least 80 g/L

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  contraindications against misoprostol
